text: This page is a list of knots. Name Image Use Alpine butterfly knot making a loop in the middle of a rope Bowline making a loop at the end of a rope Clove hitch tying a rope around an object Constrictor knot tying a rope to another rope Overhand knot Reef knot also called square knot tying two ropes together Sheet bend joining the ends of two ropes Two half-hitches attaching a rope to another object ==More reading== * * Category:Lists
